description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 min Upper Body Workout With Dumbbells (Arms, Back, Chest) Slimming & Fat Burn!' from the channel fabulous50s.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: 10 min Upper Body Workout With Dumbbells Arms, Back, Chest to lose weight & Fat Burn for women over 50 and suitable for beginners and seniors workouts. Exercises for back fat, chest toning and arms giving a perfect quick 10 minute upper body workout and if you repeat this sequence 3 times, you will have done what I would do in the gym! xx
